OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Ffading this evening, leaving a dry
OL,7,Fnight with some clear spells
OL,8,Fdeveloping across the region. Turning
OL,9,Fchilly under clear skies, especially
OL,10,Fin the countryside.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA bright start with some
OL,13,Fgood spells of sunshine. Cloud will
OL,14,Ftend to increase throughout the day,
OL,15,Fwith a few showers developing by the
OL,16,Fafternoon. Feeling warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
